# Redirect the www subdomain to the canonical apex domain.
# Cloudflare Workers static assets honor this file. For this to take effect,
# www.sunmetriclab.com must first route to the Worker (add it as a custom
# domain in the Cloudflare dashboard); the most robust alternative is a
# Cloudflare Redirect Rule at the zone level.
https://www.sunmetriclab.com/* https://sunmetriclab.com/:splat 301
